{"tid":1140918,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"其實霓虹燈牌唔難整(簡略)","createTime":"2019-05-06T06:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T07:50:59.000Z","uid":80396,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a5690a49f9ae6fc8280bda52828cb59b42dadf04","tid":1140918,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先一定唔會係生意PO，所以整D你地一定唔會買既野。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個唔算係教學，只係一個概念，有心既可以逐項研究下，每個人都可以整到，學費都唔會貴，全過程所用既野1000蚊內可以搞掂。<br />\n亦唔需要又搵工廠又搵地方，係屋企有個角落仔就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n而家所講既霓虹燈，其實同傳統好唔同。<br />\n傳統係用玻璃管燒軟，屈成唔同既形狀去造隻字出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而呢類霓虹燈，其實係一種叫「冷光條」既野，入面有兩條電線，過電就著。質地都好軟身，粗度由2mm由5mm都有，價錢都相當平。1米連電池盒大概$20左右，唔要電池盒就幾蚊雞。<br />\n<br />\n至於造型呢都有兩種主流方法<br />\n1：一條燈過，同鐵線固定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6S5Avz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6S5Avz.jpg&h=ec4e06d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2：係板材鑼條坑，將燈條塞入去。<br />\n<br />\n今次用2。<br />\n底板係用吉之島12蚊店既MDF板，質感好似超壓縮既紙皮。<br />\n過程其實冇咩好睇，純粹係電腦打隻字出黎，cap低佢轉做PNG<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3C1TiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3C1TiX.jpg&h=0eb50986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再用隻叫artcam既軟體轉做向量圖，搵返條黑白交界既邊出黎。呢條邊就係雕刻機要行既路線。<br />\n雕刻機即係呢D機。簡單呢講即係一把由電腦控制前後左右既電鑽仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yee36Gh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyee36Gh.jpg&h=df32802a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路線有，材料有，機械有，跟住就自動化了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOMYVzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOMYVzY.jpg&h=1082d7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係得出黎既結果，黑色部分既邊，就係個鑽嘴行既地方，所以最後會有一個有坑既字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXhM4tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXhM4tr.jpg&h=2cb0c7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做好左四隻字，跟住就係每條坑都鑽兩個洞，條光條後面入，前面走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bL3o6Hn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbL3o6Hn.jpg&h=7a67b0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁，一塊霓虹字燈牌就造好了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XCQMH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XCQMH7.jpg&h=4f25e589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料大約用左30蚊，時間大約1個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以點解D人咁簡單都出唔到貨</span>"},{"pid":"1eeac183d717afc1bebb1b5ec6e05afae0fa9c1f","tid":1140918,"uid":1300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeafced2de3f4554b3bc47e78f21629575797427","tid":1140918,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"快整"},{"pid":"985d6bbf0a59b0bdbf4a77a85548ccd45594cb77","tid":1140918,"uid":141823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"摩牙"},{"pid":"9b4feecf3d020a768db5f7bad825b39f38bccf05","tid":1140918,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeafced2de3f4554b3bc47e78f21629575797427","tid":1140918,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"快整"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"整好左架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe753e82da8dae16df7c8bcfd5717c3b878faa6","tid":1140918,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"邊到買到冷光條？"},{"pid":"ff36224445254d86073edef2c92979afb1471e03","tid":1140918,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebe753e82da8dae16df7c8bcfd5717c3b878faa6","tid":1140918,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"邊到買到冷光條？